{"id":274256,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-冯正虎：借款赎身的通报（五）：给胡佳/","date":"2013-01-12T11:31:06Z","modified":"2013-01-12T11:31:06Z","title":"维权网 | 冯正虎：借款赎身的通报（五）：给胡佳等人借据","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日</span><span>上午，冯正虎向上海市第二中级法院执行庭张法官缴纳了二万元罚金，并要求法院依法解除冻结账户，取出其余缴纳罚金的钱款。一周过去了，冯正虎天天电话催法官去取款，但法官不敢独立决定，要等领导研究研究。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">00</span><span>，卞、管警官又来传唤。冯正虎在五角场派出所与警察瞎聊两小时就回家。他们询问借款情况，冯正虎请他们去法院打听，因为冯正虎已依法向执行庭法官汇报并缴纳罚金了，还有一部分缴纳罚金的钱款在冻结的账户里，等他们自己解冻。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎没有钱，逼着他还；冯正虎有钱了，又怕他还。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月第一次逼冯正虎缴纳罚金时，当冯正虎转身向法官缴纳，法官却逃避了，整整追了二个月，才接受冯正虎每月一百元的缴纳。现在，冯正虎要全缴清了，他们又在担心什么？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎是借款赎身，收款后就要发出借据。已缴纳的二万元罚金，其中一部分钱款是邮政汇款的，共计</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4008.2</span><span>元人民币。邮政储蓄银行没有被冻结，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>笔邮政汇款全部提现。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>来自邮政汇款的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>个债主已确认。冯正虎向方家华、相龙杰、郑井云、刘伟、于长岭、宋以敏、胡佳、陈云飞、谭作人、陈卫、刘贤斌、孙剑婷、刘艳萍、张飞翔、徐焕章、贺任重、杨崇新、何易申、陈栋基、李国元、严伯荣、郭振河等债主致谢，并已寄发借据。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>特别向债主谭作人、陈卫、刘贤斌及其家人致敬。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎的联系方式</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>上海市政通路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span><span>弄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">302</span><span>室</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>邮编：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200433</span></div>\n<div><span>手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13524687100</span></div>\n<div><span>电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">021-55225958</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">Email</span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"mailto:fzh999net@gmail.com\">fzh999net@gmail.com</a></span></div>\n<div><span>推特：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://twitter.com/fzhenghu\">http://twitter.com/fzhenghu</a></span></div>\n<div><span>博客：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fzhenghu.net/\">http://fzhenghu.net</a></span></div>\n<div><span>督察简报：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://dcjb.info/\">http://dcjb.info</a></span></div>\n<div><span>护宪维权网</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">: <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fzh999.org/\">http://fzh999.org</a></span></div>\n<div><span>《我要立案——上海司法不作为案例汇编》</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://is.gd/aOWOOE\">http://is.gd/aOWOOE</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图：给债主胡佳的借据（沪虎借字</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">[2013]</span><span>第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0107</span><span>号）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-UE5ehG14uSo/UPEh4z0sS9I/AAAAAAAAYvg/ZAjFowvCkLU/s1600/0107.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-UE5ehG14uSo/UPEh4z0sS9I/AAAAAAAAYvg/ZAjFowvCkLU/s320/0107.jpg\" width=\"215\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab